text:
@KyivPost: #Kyiv Confirms Poisoning of Intel Chief Budanov’s Wife

Sources in the Ukrainian intelligence community have confirmed to Kyiv Post that spy chief #KyryloBudanov’s wife, #MariannaBudanova, is in hospital after being poisoned.

https://t.co/hXo5lGTII9

@KyivPost: #Russia May Use Soviet-Era #SpyPlane to Overcome Intel Black Hole

A #UK Defence Intelligence update has speculated that Russia may use the 35-year-old M-55 Mystic B aircraft to help its forces carry out reconnaissance in #Ukraine.

https://t.co/irRyG83CNR
